casebody.data:
In re Resignation of Scheub.

[Cite as In re Resignation of Scheub (1988), 40 Ohio St. 3d 609.]

(No. D.R. 88-10 Submitted December 28, 1988 Decided December 30, 1988. )

The resignation of William W. Scheub as an attorney is accepted.

Moyer, C.J., Sweeney, Locher, Holmes, Douglas, Wright and H. Brown, JJ., concur.
